result.name: Ippudo

reviews.text: Very rare a time to fine a chicken soup-based ramen.  This light clear soup with a touch of chicken is an alternative to the thick meaty pork-based soup.  I have a feeling that it cools off faster without being sticky; rather recommendable for spring-summer.

The garlic crusher is so so so dirty.
A bit expansive, but the taste is worth.

For me this was a pleasant surprise. I haven't been to Telford Gardens for ages but it seems they have done some extensive upgrading of the mall.
This includes some new restaurants including the Ippudo. It originally is from Japan and has outlets meanwhile all over the world.
Professional staff and stably-excellent quality noodles
Efficiently run, friendly enough staff. Special Karaka ramen is very good!

result.name: 一風堂

reviews.text:
假日愛人帶我去吃晚餐
點了2碗拉麵以及他以前常點的豚骨湯菠菜
上餐後他跟服務生反應菠菜量比先前的少太多
服務生態度謹慎親切
將菜湯端回廚房重新處理加量
餐後散步一會回家後我開始腹瀉
一直到今早已經拉肚子5次了……
不知道是超濃的拉麵湯頭？
還是神秘的菠菜湯？
不過店家的服務態度是值得讚賞的
包括結帳時的態度
好到讓我不相信身在香港

Very rare a time to fine a chicken soup-based ramen.  This light clear soup with a touch of chicken is an alternative to the thick meaty pork-based soup.  I have a feeling that it cools off faster without being sticky; rather recommendable for spring-summer.

The garlic crusher is so so so dirty.
A bit expansive, but the taste is worth.
味道同份量都ok, 湯底唔太鹹或油膩, 如果可以多粒蛋會更好
食品質素尚可，茶涼味怪，找位容易！
